Package: QTE.RD
Title: Quantile Treatment Effects under the Regression Discontinuity Design
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given="Zhongjun", family="Qu", email = "qu@bu.edu", role = c("aut","cph")),person(given="Jungmo", family="Yoon", email = "jmyoon@hanyang.ac.kr", role = c("aut","cre","cph")))
Author: Zhongjun Qu [aut, cph],
